	<h1 class="title">无印良品公布年报，今年中国的发展重点是家具和食品</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/343708/small/343708.jpg?1449500883" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">董芷菲 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-14 14:24:51 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/25465/medium/25465.jpg?1460611663" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


